      <title><![CDATA[Ubuntu 14.04中配置Mysql创建用户并实现远程登录]]></title>
      <url>http://echoshiki.coding.me/2016/05/28/Ubuntu-14-04%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEMysql%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%B9%B6%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="ROOT登录："><a href="#ROOT登录：" class="headerlink" title="ROOT登录："></a>ROOT登录：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mysql -u root -p19881025;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="建立数据库与用户："><a href="#建立数据库与用户：" class="headerlink" title="建立数据库与用户："></a>建立数据库与用户：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql&gt; CREATE DATABASE wordpress;</span><br><span class="line">mysql&gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON wordpress.* TO echoshiki@localhost IDENTIFIED BY <span class="string">"19881025"</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="赋予该用户任何机器远程登录的权限："><a href="#赋予该用户任何机器远程登录的权限：" class="headerlink" title="赋予该用户任何机器远程登录的权限："></a>赋予该用户任何机器远程登录的权限：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql&gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON wordpress.* TO echoshiki@<span class="string">"%"</span> IDENTIFIED BY <span class="string">"19881025"</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="修改mysql配置，注释点本地监听："><a href="#修改mysql配置，注释点本地监听：" class="headerlink" title="修改mysql配置，注释点本地监听："></a>修改mysql配置，注释点本地监听：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vi /etc/mysql/my.cnf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#bind-address = 127.0.0.1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="重启服务："><a href="#重启服务：" class="headerlink" title="重启服务："></a>重启服务：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo restart mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
